ZH: 我听到一个尖叫声，好像是在救援的时候。
EN: I heard a scream, as if someone was calling for help.

ZH: 这个恐怖电影会让人尖叫。
EN: This horror movie will make people scream.

ZH: 小孩子看到爬山虎就会尖叫。
EN: Children will scream when they see a climbing ivy.

ZH: 当她看到一只老鼠时，她惊恐地尖叫起来。
EN: She screamed in terror when she saw a mouse.

ZH: 那个可怕的噪音让我尖叫了一声。
EN: That awful noise made me let out a scream.

ZH: 当他摔倒的时候，他发出了一声尖叫。
EN: He let out a scream when he fell down.

ZH: 姐姐吓到了，突然尖叫起来。
EN: My sister got scared and suddenly screamed.

ZH: 我们看到那个鬼屋时，大家都尖叫了起来。
EN: We all screamed when we saw that haunted house.

ZH: 她的惊喜让她尖叫了一声。
EN: Her surprise made her burst into a scream.

ZH: 当他们看到吓人的情景时，他们不禁尖叫起来。
EN: They couldn't help but scream when they saw the scary scene.

ZH: 女孩子们在过山车上高声尖叫。
EN: The girls screamed loudly on the roller coaster.

ZH: 当那个蜘蛛爬到他的腿上时，他尖叫了起来。
EN: He screamed when the spider crawled onto his leg.

ZH: 当听到好消息时，她高兴得尖叫起来。
EN: She screamed in joy when she heard the good news.

ZH: 汽车突然停下来，引起了一阵尖叫声。
EN: The sudden stop of the car caused a scream.

