EN: This horror movie is sure to provoke screams from the audience.

ZH: 当恐怖的画面出现时，人们不禁尖叫起来。
EN: People couldn't help but scream when the terrifying image appeared.

ZH: 我们在游乐园的过山车上尖叫个不停。
EN: We screamed ceaselessly on the roller coaster at the amusement park.

ZH: 她的尖叫声吓坏了我，我差点从座位上跳起来。
EN: Her scream scared me so much I almost jumped out of my seat.

ZH: 在悬念的片尾，观众发出一阵尖叫声。
EN: The audience let out a scream during the suspenseful ending.

ZH: 他的恶作剧把她弄得尖叫不止。
EN: He played a prank on her that made her scream non-stop.
